tweet_text: BREAKING: Multiple large explosions near the White House, amid escalating George Floyd demonstrations. #GeorgeFloydProtests

Incredible. honoring the death of #GeorgeFloyd and the #BLM movement by blacking out programming on channels for 8 minutes and 45 seconds. With the text "I can not breathe" and ways to donate to causes that need our help.
Not once did Trump mention justice for George Floyd in his speech, but I can not say i am surprised about that

Donald Trump continues to be disgusting and outrageous. He may regretfully be a temporary Ward 2 resident, but his actions and statements are fundamentally antithetical to the values of our community. #BlackLivesMatter

After what we saw yesterday afternoon at #LafayettePark it is apparent we are all #GeorgeFloyd in trump is opinion. An overwhelming rejection of the GOP must be delivered at each #Primary and in #November2020. Freedom is in jeopardy. #AllLivesMatter
